videos.headline: McDonald drills step-back triple for Arizona
videos.description: Aari McDonald steps behind the 3-point line and knocks down the shot from deep to give Arizona an early lead vs. Indiana.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (McDonald drills step-back triple for Arizona) 2021/3/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Indiana's Patberg dishes no-look dime
videos.description: Indiana takes its first lead of the game after Ali Patberg sends a sweet pass to Mackenzie Holmes for a basket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Indiana's Patberg dishes no-look dime) 2021/3/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baptiste's 3-ball extends Arizona's lead
videos.description: Arizona whips the ball around the perimeter to get a wide-open look for Trinity Baptiste, who knocks down a 3 to give the Wildcats an eight-point lead.

videos.headline: Tempers flare between Indiana, Arizona after hard foul
videos.description: The Hoosiers and Wilcats get tangled up under the hoop after Indiana's Ali Patberg is knocked to the ground.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Tempers flare between Indiana, Arizona after hard foul) 2021/3/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: McDonald rattles home 3 to keep Arizona on top
videos.description: Aari McDonald maneuvers around a screen and connects on a 3-pointer to put the Wildcats ahead by seven.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (McDonald rattles home 3 to keep Arizona on top) 2021/3/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pueyo's heads-up touch pass helps Arizona break the press in style
videos.description: Helena Pueyo beats a defender to the ball and slaps it to Bendu Yeaney for the basket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Pueyo's heads-up touch pass helps Arizona break the press in style) 2021/3/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arizona celebrates after earning first Final Four in program history
videos.description: After defeating Indiana 66-53, Arizona players and coaches storm the court together in jubilation.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Arizona celebrates after earning first Final Four in program history) 2021/3/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: McDonald turns steal into and-1 bucket to seal Arizona's win
videos.description: Aari McDonald rips the ball away for a steal and then scores through contact on the other end to help Arizona defeat Indiana.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (McDonald turns steal into and-1 bucket to seal Arizona's win) 2021/3/29 ESHEET
